!!【柯林斯英汉双解大词典】

:<div>

rely /rɪˈlaɪ/

(relying,relied,relies) 

1. V-I If you rely on someone or something, you need them and depend on them in order to live or work properly. 依赖; 依靠 

例： They relied heavily on the advice of their professional advisers. 他们非常依赖专业顾问的建议。 

2. V-I If you can rely on someone to work well or to behave as you want them to, you can trust them to do this. 信任; 信赖 

例： I know I can rely on you to sort it out. 我知道我可以信赖你来处理此事。

</div>

